Give your dining room a peppy twist with this simple yet classic 6 piece dinner set from Corelle. The set contains a partition plate a small bowl a medium bowl 2 spoons and a fork. It is crafted from glass and has cartoon prints.

  • Category: Home Ware
  • Type: Dinner Set
  • Colour: White Green
  • Design: Cartoon prints
  • Contents: 1 partition plate 1 small bowl 1 medium bowl 2 spoons and a fork
  • Other Features: Dishwasher and Microwave safe

Care Tips
Wash with warm soapy water
Rinse and dry thoroughly
For removal of stubborn residues allow the dish to cool partially fill with warm soapy water and allow it to soak for 10 to 20 minutes
